snippet.title: Log Jammers Upmake - PC/Console Trailer - Mega Cat Studios Video Game
snippet.description:
Find some flannel and pack your adrenaline for this action-packed, horror sports tragedy.  The stakes are high, and the multi-species cheerleaders are jumping higher.

Wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/684800/Log_Jammers/
